<div class='container'>
  <ul class='gstart pager' id="getStarted">
      <li class='gstart active' id='stepOne'>Step One</li>
      <li class='gstart' id='stepTwo'>Step Two</li>
      <li class='gstart' id='stepThree'>Step Three</li>
  </ul>
  <div class='row formHolder'>
    <div class='col-md-6 col-md-offset-3' id='formHolder'>
      <div class='formDiv' id="divOne">
        <h2 class='formHeader' id="tabTwo">Enable Monitoring</h2>
        <p>Follow the link below to authorize Shift to monitor your Gmail for inactivity</p>
        <div class='ellipse inline-block'>
          <div class='circle inline-block'>
          </div>
        </div>
        <%= link_to "Activate Passive Monitoring", '/auth/google_oauth2', :target => "_blank" %>
      </div>
      <div class='formDiv' id="divTwo">
        <h2 class='formHeader' id="tabOne">Build Support Network</h2>
        <p>Set up your support by completing the form below to add a someone to your support network.</p>
        <%= render "supporters/form", locals: {user: @user} %>
      </div>
      <div class='formDiv' id="divThree">
        <h2 class='formHeader' id="tabThree">Setup Notifications</h2>
        <p>If you go inactive, what would message would you like your support network to get? Fill out the form below to set a inactivity duration and a message that will be sent.</p>
        <%= render "triggers/new", locals: {user: @user} %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='row' id='<%=@user.id%>'>
    <div class='col-md-3' id='backButton'><h3>Go Back</h3></div>
    <div class='col-md-3 col-md-offset-6' id='nextButton'><h3>Next Step</h3></div>
  </div>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-xs-6' id='network'>
      <h3>Your Support</h3>
    </div>
    <div class='col-xs-6' id='notifications'>
      <h3>Your Notifications</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
